Katie Montgomery, of St. Pat's, bumps a ball against Maxwell on Saturday in North Platte. (Derek Noehren / The North Platte Telegraph) Posted: Saturday, October 10, 2015 2:44 pm | Updated: 5:34 pm, Sat Oct 10, 2015. St. Pat's tops Maxwell, Hershey in tri By DEREK NOEHREN dnoehren@nptelegraph.com nptelegraph.com 
An early wakeup call was no problem for the Lady Irish volleyball team on Saturday as they cruised to a 2-0 record as host of a triangular with Hershey and Maxwell. 
St. Pat’s (14-7) made quick work of Maxwell (6-14) in the first game, which began at 9 a.m., winning 25-11, 25-15. The Irish followed that with a 25-12, 23-25, 25-12 victory over rival Hershey (11-10).     Subscription required
